OL,3,C'My Son's A Queer' actor and TikToker
OL,4,CRob Madge on redefining the word
OL,5,C'queer'
OL,7,FITV News Central's Hannah Ludlow sat
OL,8,Fdown with Rob and their parents to
OL,9,Fhear about their UK tour and love for
OL,10,Fthe Midlands.
OL,12,FRob Madge (they/them) might have
OL,13,Fbecome a West End star and social
OL,14,Fmedia sensation in recent years, but
OL,15,Fthe actor's love of performing did not
OL,16,Fstart on a stage.
