OL,3,C'My Son's A Queer' actor and TikToker
OL,4,CRob Madge on redefining the word
OL,5,C'queer'
OL,7,FIt was in their family's living room
OL,8,Fthat Rob first discovered a talent for
OL,9,Fsinging, dancing and acting - and it's
OL,10,Fin that very room that I sit down with
OL,11,FRob and their parents to discuss their
OL,12,Fone-person play 'My Son's A Queer'.
OL,14,FRob wrote the play during lockdown,
OL,15,Fand it has since been enjoyed by
OL,16,Faudiences in London and Edinburgh. Now
OL,17,Fit is embarking on it's first tour
OL,18,Facross the UK, starting in the
OL,19,FMidlands, where Rob grew up.
