OL,7,FThe tour will open at Leicester's
OL,8,FCurve Theatre on Monday 8 July, before
OL,9,Fheading to Birmingham, Coventry,
OL,10,FLiverpool, Derby, Edinburgh and
OL,11,FManchester.
OL,13,FDescribing the play, Rob, who grew up
OL,14,Fin Swadlincote in Derbyshire, says:
OL,15,F"My Son's A Queer is the true story of
OL,16,Fmy family, who helped me put on shows
OL,17,Fin my living room every weekend.
