OL,4,CRob Madge on redefining the word
OL,5,C'queer'
OL,7,F"In this show we see a Disney parade
OL,8,Fthat happened in that hallway over
OL,9,Fthere in 2009 and it went hideously
OL,10,Fwrong.
OL,12,F"Dad was the stage manager, he got all
OL,13,Fthe costumes in the wrong order, the
OL,14,Fstage broke and it was a nightmare."
OL,16,FThey added: "In My Son's A Queer I, at
OL,17,Fthe age of 27, am going to be
OL,18,Frecreating this Disney parade and it's
OL,19,Fgoing to go right, and we're going to
OL,20,Fwork out where Dad went wrong.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/13
