OL,4,CRob Madge on redefining the word
OL,5,C'queer'
OL,7,F"Ultimately, it's about realising that
OL,8,FI've been very lucky to have had (my
OL,9,Fparents) supporting me in not just
OL,10,Fliving room shows but in my identity,
OL,11,Fmy career and my whole life really.
OL,13,F"The message I want to get out there
OL,14,Fis how easy it is to love your child
OL,15,Funconditionally."
OL,17,FSo why did they choose to perform at
OL,18,Fso many venues in the Midlands?
