OL,3,C'My Son's A Queer' actor and TikToker
OL,4,CRob Madge on redefining the word
OL,5,C'queer'
OL,7,FRob says: "It's my absolute heartbeat,
OL,8,FI always come back whenever I can. I
OL,9,Fmoved out but did I ever really? I'm
OL,10,Fhere every other weekend going to the
OL,11,Fpub.
OL,13,F"It's the sense of humour, it's the
OL,14,Frealness and it keeps you really
OL,15,Fgrounded. You can be off doing what
OL,16,Fyou think is the most amazing West End
OL,17,Frun, you go to the pub and people are
OL,18,Fmore interested in who's winning the
OL,19,Fbonus ball for the Euros and it's
OL,20,Flovely.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G6/13
