OL,4,CRob Madge on redefining the word
OL,5,C'queer'
OL,7,F"And for anybody that can't access the
OL,8,FWest End I think it's really important
OL,9,Fthat a show like this can be seen by
OL,10,Fsomebody that might not be able to get
OL,11,Fdown to London."
OL,13,FRob says the chance to perform at the
OL,14,FBirmingham Hippodrome will hold a
OL,15,Fspecial place in their heart.
OL,17,F"The Birmingham Hippodrome is my
OL,18,Fchildhood theatre so to do 'My Son's A
OL,19,FQueer' there, I'm really excited.
