OL,4,CRob Madge on redefining the word
OL,5,C'queer'
OL,7,F"We'd go every Christmas and we'd see
OL,8,Fthe pantomime and we'd see people like
OL,9,FJulian Clary and there was something
OL,10,Fin him specifically - this flamboyant
OL,11,Fcharacter that could wear the most
OL,12,Famazing outfits and still get a laugh
OL,13,F- that stuck with me at a very early
OL,14,Fage."
OL,16,FRob's parents, Janice and Jon Madge,
OL,17,Fsay they are incredibly proud of them.
OL,19,FJon says: "We've always said that good
OL,20,Fcomedy is that good that it will make
OL,21,Fyou laugh and it'll make you cry.
