OL,7,FThe amount of tears that were shed
OL,8,Foutside of the theatre after Rob's
OL,9,Ffirst few shows - for us, although
OL,10,Fit's the norm, there are people out
OL,11,Fthere who didn't get that treatment.
OL,12,FWho didn't get that support.
OL,14,F"I took Rob to the football, to the
OL,15,Fcricket, the rugby, but Rob didn't
OL,16,Flike any of that. I was trying to
OL,17,Fchannel Rob down the route that I
OL,18,Fthought Rob would enjoy, but that
OL,19,Fwasn't for them."
