OL,7,FRob's mum Janice adds: "I never
OL,8,Fthought 'Rob's destined for stardom'
OL,9,Fbut they've just progressed and
OL,10,Fprogressed.
OL,12,F"And a lot of that isn't just talent,
OL,13,Fit's determination and if you've got a
OL,14,Fdrive and you always push and push and
OL,15,Fpush through failure and rejection, I
OL,16,Fthink then anybody in whatever the
OL,17,Ffield is, will make it."
