OL,4,CRob Madge on redefining the word
OL,5,C'queer'
OL,7,FOn their decision to include the word
OL,8,F'Queer' in the play's title, Rob says:
OL,9,F"I want to demystify how frightening
OL,10,Fthe word can be and rightfully so, I
OL,11,Fdon't want to undermine people's fear
OL,12,Fof that word.
OL,14,F"It can be redefined as happiness and
OL,15,Fjoy and pride and celebration.
