OL,3,C'My Son's A Queer' actor and TikToker
OL,4,CRob Madge on redefining the word
OL,5,C'queer'
OL,7,F"Over time I've learned that all the
OL,8,Fthings that hold you back are the
OL,9,Fthings that you're going to end up
OL,10,Fbeing celebrated for, and the things
OL,11,Fthat you're most terrified of are
OL,12,Fgoing to be the things that make life
OL,13,Fworth living."
OL,15,F'My Son's A Queer' has earned a
OL,16,FWhatsOnStage award and an Olivier
OL,17,Faward nomination since opening at the
OL,18,FTurbine Theatre in 2021.
